===Verb===
'''Pistolwhip'''
#To [[strike]] with a [[pistol]]. Especially with the [[butt]].

===Examples===
Future tense: "He broke your [[pistol]]? What are you going to do? You can't shoot him with it." "No, but I can pistolwhip him until he runs out of [[stupid]]."

Present tense: "What are you doing?" "I'm pistolwhipping this poor [[sod]] for being an [[idiot]]."

Past tense: "Remember when I pistolwhipped you for breaking my [[firearm]]?"